Metadata: Ocean and Coastal Law Memo (Issue 33, October 1989)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
One newsletter issue for 1989. For previous issue (s), see: ORESU-N-88-003. Previous name of newsletter was Ocean Law Memo.

Beginning with this issue, the formerly separate publications Ocean Law Memo and Coastal Law memo have been combined into one newsletter publication entitled Ocean and Coastal Law Memo. Main topic in this issue is: Recent Developments in Ocean and Coastal Law, 1988. International Developments, N. C. Skinner.
